fields.name: Classic Pancakes
fields.cooking_instructions: Mix flour, milk, eggs, and baking powder. Cook on a hot griddle until golden brown.

fields.name: Spaghetti Bolognese
fields.cooking_instructions: Cook spaghetti. In a separate pan, cook ground beef with tomato sauce and spices. Mix together and serve.

fields.name: Chicken Caesar Salad
fields.cooking_instructions: Grill chicken. Toss with lettuce, Caesar dressing, croutons, and parmesan cheese.

fields.name: Beef Tacos
fields.cooking_instructions: Cook ground beef with taco seasoning. Serve in tortillas with toppings of choice.

fields.name: Vegetable Stir-Fry
fields.cooking_instructions: Stir-fry mixed vegetables in a wok with soy sauce and garlic. Serve over rice.

fields.name: Chocolate Chip Cookies
fields.cooking_instructions: Mix butter, sugar, eggs, flour, and chocolate chips. Bake at 350Â°F for 10-12 minutes.
